# ğŸ¯ Target-based ARM Syllabus (ALSA / ASoC focused)

Main syllabus ko **6 phases** me divide kar raha hoon.
Har phase directly **audio driver se connected** hai.

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 0 â€“ Baseline (1 week)

*(Agar ye already aata hai to skip)*

- Linux kernel basics
- `initcall`, `module_init`
- `platform_driver`
- `/proc`, `/sys`, `/dev`
- `printk`, `dynamic debug`

ğŸ“Œ **Goal:** Kernel me comfortable feel karna

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 1 â€“ ARM System Overview (1â€“2 weeks)

### Topics

- ARMv8-A overview (Raspberry Pi 4 = Cortex-A72)

- ARM vs x86 (big picture)

- SoC kya hota hai (CPU + peripherals)

- Boot flow:

  ```
  GPU â†’ Bootloader â†’ Kernel â†’ init
  ```

### ALSA link

- Kernel kab audio driver load karta hai
- Device Tree kab parse hoti hai

ğŸ“Œ **Must understand diagrams**, ratta nahi

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 2 â€“ Memory System (ğŸ”¥ Very Important) (2 weeks)

### Topics

- Physical vs Virtual memory
- MMIO (ioremap, readl/writel)
- Cache basics:
  - I-cache / D-cache
  - Cache coherency
- Memory barriers:
  - `mb()`, `rmb()`, `wmb()`

### ALSA / ASoC link

- DMA buffer corruption issues
- Crackling / noise root cause
- Why `dma_alloc_coherent()` needed

ğŸ“Œ **Audio bugs ka 50% yahin se aata hai**

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 3 â€“ Interrupts & Timing (2 weeks)

### Topics

- ARM GIC (Generic Interrupt Controller)
- IRQ vs FIQ
- Interrupt latency
- SoftIRQ, Tasklet, Workqueue
- High resolution timers

### ALSA link

- PCM period interrupts
- XRUNs (underrun/overrun)
- IRQ storm debugging

ğŸ“Œ Agar yeh clear ho gaya â†’ audio glitches samajh aa jaate hain

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 4 â€“ ARM Peripherals & SoC buses (2â€“3 weeks)

### Topics

- AMBA bus
  - AXI
  - APB
- I2S / PCM hardware blocks
- Clock framework (CCF)
- Reset controller

### ALSA / ASoC link

- `set_sysclk()`
- BCLK / LRCLK issues
- Sample rate mismatch

ğŸ“Œ ASoC machine driver yahin connect hota hai

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 5 â€“ Device Tree (ARM style) (2 weeks)

### Topics

- DTS vs DTB vs DTBO
- `compatible`, `reg`, `interrupts`
- `clocks`, `resets`
- Audio graph bindings

### ALSA link

- `simple-audio-card`
- Codec vs CPU DAI mapping
- Why sound card not visible

ğŸ“Œ **ALSA + ARM ka bridge**

------

## ğŸ”¹ Phase 6 â€“ ARM Power & Performance (1â€“2 weeks)

### Topics

- CPUfreq / cpuidle
- Clock gating
- Runtime PM
- DMA latency vs power

### ALSA link

- Audio pop / click on suspend-resume
- HDMI audio delay
- Bluetooth audio stutter

